Package edu.cnm.deepdive.dungeonrun.model.entity

Class Attempt

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.dungeonrun.model.entity.Attempt
  • @Entity
public class Attempt
extends Object
    Attempt entity to hold the database of attempts generated and completed. Indexes for difficulty and endTime will be indexed since this is a metric that will be used for the implementation of leaderboards.
